{"tid":162483,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實學英文背文章有冇用","createTime":"2017-03-19T10:29:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-19T12:13:48.000Z","uid":80481,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"35d0285833abd80e291f0dca0b05ff334ab87387","tid":162483,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:29:51.000Z","msg":"form 3之後學校就冇叫我哋背默，得默單字，單字默完好多都唔記得曬，或者淨係認得出意思，但作文多數都用唔返，只係用返比較簡單嘅字表達返個意思"},{"pid":"8d27a86529308fef6612f21e3bba404f0dfad8d9","tid":162483,"uid":69168,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:30:58.000Z","msg":"好過認都認唔到隻字啦"},{"pid":"585e11bcf1a0353801a74a68bf8f97c9c5e29055","tid":162483,"uid":59746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:32:00.000Z","msg":"中四開始習慣成篇5** 範文背<br />\n利申英文5*"},{"pid":"9ad5fe7ae5030a6e280e443875b8e716145625fd","tid":162483,"uid":80481,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:35:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中四開始習慣成篇5** 範文背<br />\n利申英文5*</blockquote><br />\n我係今年dse考生，恐怕都係慳返時間背難字好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e5d7a67f6a485ab9cdd3e50307df78fd4ad7742","tid":162483,"uid":69792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:37:39.000Z","msg":"一味剩係識背，又唔考究背後意思，就算比你默得返成篇文出嚟都冇用啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n難怪香港人學咗咁耐英文，啲英文都係咁屎<br />\n除咗背個句phrase，更加要學習如何應用，睇多啲英文節目，聽得多睇得多，然後再試下運用，自自然就會慢慢進步"},{"pid":"a339624603765c0d6fd5de315ec852a22b380b79","tid":162483,"uid":92600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T10:41:57.000Z","msg":"我覺得背都幾有用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bcd461a9a62e0cdc7873850f427192e594d814d","tid":162483,"uid":53254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-19T11:00:47.000Z","msg":"背得幾多"},{"pid":"42f549639b9853b486e4d4240dc4ec9fa74ecbd2"